An ornate circular table, surrounded by large, upholstered chairs dominates the planning room.  Hanging from the ceiling is a well-polished crystal chandelier.  Banners of red and gold, worked with the insignia of the House, hang from the walls.  An elaborately framed painting dominates one wall.
